          "WELCHER (which) asks about specific items:",
          "",
          "DECLENSION (same as 'dieser'):",
          "          Masc     Fem      Neut     Plural",
          "NOM:      welcher  welche   welches  welche",
          "AKK:      welchen  welche   welches  welche",
          "DAT:      welchem  welcher  welchem  welchen",
          "",
          "EXAMPLES:",
          "Welcher Bus fährt nach Berlin?",
          "(Which bus goes to Berlin?)",
          "",
          "Welche Farbe magst du?",
          "(Which color do you like?)",
          "",
          "Welches Buch liest du?",
          "(Which book are you reading?)",
          "",
          "WAS FÜR EIN (what kind of):",
          "Was für ein Auto hast du?",
          "(What kind of car do you have?)"
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Lektion einundzwanzig"
      }
    ]
